cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for sentence classification. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also uses neural networks, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. Additionally, the paper involves techniques such as structured prediction and contextual information, which are relevant to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also deals with information retrieval and classification, which are relevant to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
